  "description": "Rat immunoglobulin heavy chain locus on chr6q32 (telomeric end), ~2 Mb in proximal-to-distal V-D-J-C order. ~200 VH gene segments (functional + pseudo), ~10 DH, 6 JH, then constant region with IGHM, IGHD, IGHG2c/2a/2b/1, IGHE, IGHA. Rat Igh contains 4 IGHG paralogs (90-95% identity) \u2014 direct analog to human IGHG cluster. VDJ somatic recombination and class-switch produce structural heterogeneity.",
